data.title: 3201 Danville Blvd, Alamo, California
data.meta_description: Specialties: Lodestar Private Asset Management is an independent, fee-only Financial Planning and Wealth Management firm based in Alamo, CA. We have a deep knowledge of the various tools of money, including stock options and restricted shares, deferred comp and pension plans, real estate investments, debt instruments, and tax shelters. That technical knowledge is balanced with a respectful awareness of the emotional influence that money exerts. We focus on providing clear, expert and unbiased financial advice tailored to each client's unique situation. Established in 1989.  We provide tailored financial planning and asset management to people who recognize the value of expert advice and guidance. We are compensated only by our clients - not the investment funds, products, companies, or other professionals we might leverage.
